		PSYCHIC PURIFICATION:

	The psychic is able to go into a meditative trance. When in this trance
    he can slow down his body's metabolism, slowing the effects of poison and
    drugs. He can expel the poisons and drugs from his body entirely.

	EFFECT: remove poison and intoxication, while in a meditative trance
	POISON: add_poison(-10) and reduce intoxication(-3) every 15 seconds
	COST: 40 sp
